{"tid":2034873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會預留30小時審議國歌法　料下周四完成","createTime":"2020-05-25T13:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T14:01:16.000Z","uid":153689,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"484bee0cbfd40e0a95d62ff0f6ee989a423f02ea","tid":2034873,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】《國歌條例草案》周三立法會大會恢復二讀，主席梁君彥已預留約30小時審議，預計下周四完成。<br />\n<br />\n立法會外一帶加強布防，被大量水馬圍封至中信大廈外一段龍匯道，出入口有警員駐守。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥指已決定，就所有條文及修正案，進行合併辯論，並預留四日共30小時處理，預計下星期四完成審議及表決。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，由於修正案內容不可改變國歌法基本原則，只可更改國歌法在香港實施的細節，因此由12名民主派議員提交共49項修正案，最終只批出22項，包括由陳志全提出要求教育學生國歌作曲及作詞人生平及死因。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣告"},{"pid":"505d77889c293760523635558d5bc01ca4b87e0e","tid":2034873,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392204&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3kn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=47ae3c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392204&h=335ad446\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392204</a>"},{"pid":"fb98138acc3c115bc86260e19d51381f7666d61b","tid":2034873,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:43:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0f6381bcad4e0e3a53974a834f7bd621c626983","tid":2034873,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"咁527點？"},{"pid":"83dce25ce8ed1d22b6d27570d25022b2b3fda6aa","tid":2034873,"uid":104845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0GJCXy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0GJCXy.png&h=77555016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img 